VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT DisabledTrustEvaluator\s*\(\s*\)|trustAllCertificates|serverTrustManager\s*=\s*nil
WHEN EXPR MISSING:test|development|localhost|staging|PinnedCertificatesTrustEvaluator|RevocationTrustEvaluator
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects Alamofire configurations that disable TLS server trust evaluation.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for ServerTrustEvaluating Disabled with DisabledTrustEvaluator.
